shape: sequence_diagram

Client: Client
NotificationService: Notification Service
TemplateEngine: Template Engine
ChannelHandler: Channel Handler
Provider: External Provider
WebhookHandler: Webhook Handler
Analytics: Analytics Service

Client -> NotificationService: Submit notification request
NotificationService -> NotificationService: Validate request
NotificationService -> NotificationService: Route to channel
NotificationService -> TemplateEngine: Request template render
TemplateEngine -> NotificationService: Return rendered content
NotificationService -> ChannelHandler: Send notification
ChannelHandler -> Provider: Deliver via channel
Provider -> WebhookHandler: Delivery status update
WebhookHandler -> NotificationService: Update delivery status
NotificationService -> Analytics: Record metrics
NotificationService -> Client: Return tracking ID

